                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870110-22-off116 t17870110-22-cd117"></join>, three linen table-cloths, value 15 s. two aprons, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870110-22-victim234" type="victimName">
                     Francis 
                     Hayward
